## Overview

Phase 4.5 implements the gameplay loop that transforms the RPG system from a
passive simulation into an **interactive simulation RPG engine**:

```
Scene → Player Action → Simulation Mutation → New World State → New Scenes
```

This completes the core gameplay loop, enabling players to directly influence
the world simulation through structured actions.

